import React from "react";
import { UserPhotoContainer } from "../userIcon/userIcon.style";
import {
  SearchContainer,
  SearchButtonContainer,
  SearchInputContainer,
} from "./Search.style";

const Search = () => {
  return (
    <SearchContainer>
      <SearchInputContainer
        class="searchInput"
        type="text"
        name=""
        placeholder="Search"
      />
      <SearchButtonContainer>
        <UserPhotoContainer>
          <svg
            width="50"
            height="51"
            viewBox="0 0 50 51"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M48 15.8228C48 23.4569 41.8113 29.6456 34.1772 29.6456C26.5431 29.6456 20.3544 23.4569 20.3544 15.8228C20.3544 8.18867 26.5431 2 34.1772 2C41.8113 2 48 8.18867 48 15.8228Z"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="4"
            />
            <line
              x1="24.2423"
              y1="26.8354"
              x2="2.09036"
              y2="48.3544"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="6"
            />
          </svg>
        </UserPhotoContainer>
      </SearchButtonContainer>
    </SearchContainer>
  );
};
export default Search;
